 Zinoleesky, a fast-rising musician, refutes claims that he is 27 years old, following a public controversy about the singer’s true age. This follows a debate on Twitter about the singer’s age, with admirers validating their claims by citing the singer’s contact with Naira Marley. READ MORE: Naira Marley Signs Zinoleesky, Mohbad, Cblack And Fabian to Marlian Music “Honestly still surprised that Zinoleesky is 27. I thought he was like 19,” a Twitter user wrote. The artist responds by revealing his true age as 22 and dispelling rumors that he is neither 19 nor 27 in a video posted to his Instagram story page. See post below:   A post shared by Sabi Radio (@sabiradio)   